    <!-- Abstract -->
    <abstract>
      <para>
        This dataset compiles georeferenced occurrence records for the rare chalk‐loving plant 
        <italic>Linaria cretacea</italic> Fisch. ex Spreng. from digitized herbarium specimens in Kazakhstan (AA), Russia (LE, MW) and Ukraine (KW), supplemented by field surveys in the Aktobe Region (2010–2012, 2020–2022). Records include collection date, locality, habitat description, and collector. Data are formatted in Darwin Core and intended for botanical, conservation, and biogeographical analyses.
      </para>
    </abstract>

