    <!-- Methods summary -->
    <methods>
      <methodStep>
        <description>
          Herbarium specimen data were digitized from AA (Kazakhstan), LE and MW (Russia), KW (Ukraine) and verified via GBIF and POWO. Field surveys in Aktobe Region (2010–2012, 2020–2022) included GPS georeferencing, photographic documentation, and voucher collection. Records were standardized to Darwin Core, checked in QGIS, and assembled into occurrence.csv.
        </description>
      </methodStep>
    </methods>

